FW: All firmware code
   Algorithm : code the algorithms and their context header file. 
   Mellanox : the CC shell - the Mellanox private wrapper
   include : all include files required to compile the algorithms
           platform : contains all supported platforms
                    x86_64 : the simulator code
                    irisc : for compiling IRISC code
                    riscv : for compiling RISCV code
